summary: Frontend testing for Dynasty Spas color selector and new product models. All requested features verified working correctly.

ui_bugs.issue: Product image not loading in screenshot - may be CDN timing or image URL issue

passed_tests: Dynasty Spas page loads with all 19 products including new models: Bay Bliss, High Tide, Bahama Royale, Imperial Royale
Dynasty color selector on product pages: Shell Color and Skirt Color sections display correctly with bigger swatches (w-20 h-20)
Dynasty shell colors working: Sterling Marble, Storm Clouds, Tuscan Sun, Smoky Mountain with real CDN images
Dynasty skirt colors working: Black Confer, Gray Confer, Ash Elite, Coastal Gray Elite with real CDN images
Dynasty color selection updates 'Your Selection' summary correctly showing Shell: [name], Skirt: [name]
Dynasty products use 'Skirt Color' label instead of 'Cabinet Color' (brand-specific)
Swim Spas page loads all Dynasty swim spa models: 11' Family Island Oasis SL, 13' Aquex Party, 13' Aquex Pro, 13' Aquex Pro Plus, 16' Aquex Trainer, 17' Aquex Pro Plus
Dynasty Spas Swim Spas section header appears on Swim Spas page
Viking Spas 3-part color selector working: Shell Color, Cabinet Color, Corner Color
Viking shell colors: White, Silver, Opal (3 options)
Viking Elite cabinet colors: Slate, Chestnut, Stone, Carbon (4 options)
Viking corner color options: Match Cabinet, Carbon (2 options)
Compare Models feature works on Dynasty products - dropdown shows all other Dynasty models with specs
Compare Models feature shows side-by-side comparison with specs: Dimensions, Seats, Jets, Seating, Electrical, Water Capacity
Quick Overview table shows all Dynasty models with View links
Existing Dynasty models verified: Coconut Bay II/III, Paradise Bay III, Caribbean Breeze
Viking Swim Spas appear on Swim Spas page: Valhalla, Asgard, Odin, Thor
critical_code_review_comments: Dynasty color selector uses unified getShellColorData/getCabinetColorData functions that correctly fall back to DYNASTY_SHELL_COLORS and DYNASTY_CABINET_COLORS from products.js
Dynasty swatches are correctly sized w-20 h-20 (bigger than other brands' w-14 h-14)
Dynasty products correctly show 'Skirt Color' label instead of 'Cabinet Color'
Full color names displayed correctly for Dynasty products (e.g., 'Sterling Marble' not truncated)
Viking Spas 3-part selector (shell, cabinet, corner) implemented correctly
Compare Models feature uses comparableModels memo to filter products by brand
seed_data_creation: N/A - All product data hardcoded in frontend/src/data/products.js
context_for_next_testing_agent: Dynasty color selector fully working: (1) Shell colors with real Dynasty CDN images (sterlingMarble, stormClouds, tuscanSun, smokyMountain). (2) Cabinet/Skirt colors with real Dynasty CDN images (blackConfer, grayConfer, ashElite, coastalGrayElite). (3) Your Selection summary updates on click. (4) Dynasty uses 'Skirt Color' label.
